Field Required Type Description
code required number This is the same as the HTTP status of the response.
errors required Array<ErrorDetail> A list of errors which occurred. Each error contains an identifier for the type of error and a short description.See ErrorDetail for more information.
message required string A short description of the error.
details optional Array<ErrorDetail> Additional details about the error.See ErrorDetail for more information.
status optional string A status code that indicates the error type.
